# Starlight docs (`apps/public-docs`)

Unified user documentation for `docs.newsfork.com` — API reference, guides, user manual, legal policies, and company info.

## Content paths

- Documentation pages live under `apps/public-docs/src/content/docs/`.
- Korean locale: `apps/public-docs/src/content/docs/ko/`.
- Each sidebar `autogenerate` directory should have an `index.md` or `index.mdx` with frontmatter `title`.

## Sidebar sections

| Directory | Purpose |
| --- | --- |
| `getting-started.md`, `manual-setup.md`, `changelog.md` | Start Here |
| `v1/api/` | REST API reference |
| `v1/guides/` | Integration and architecture guides (no internal engineering guides) |
| `user-manual/` | End-user manual |
| `reference/` | Conventions and reference material |
| `legal/` | Privacy, terms, cookies, acceptable use |
| `company/` | About, contact |
| `resources/` | FAQ, glossary |

Internal engineering guides live in `core-platform/docs/devdocs` (`nl-internal-docs`).

## Deploy

Production deploys to Cloudflare Pages project `nl-public-docs` via `.github/workflows/deploy-public-docs.yml`.
